Lisa Gormley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_Gormley 0 Lisa Gormley (born 29 September 1984) is an English-born Australian actress and best known for playing Bianca Scott on the Channel 7 serial drama Home and Away. She is a NIDA graduate. Lisa_Gormley ( born_29_September_1984 ) is an_English-born_Australian_actress and best_known for playing Bianca_Scott on the_Channel_7_serial_drama_Home and Away .
